01:09:43,718 --> 01:09:45,218
- Whoo!
- Thorns! Thorns!

1575
01:09:45,243 --> 01:09:47,797
Thorns mengamankan tiket
ke babak 4 Besar

1576
01:09:47,822 --> 01:09:49,572
<i>dan menuju ke playoff.</i>

1577
01:09:49,597 --> 01:09:51,916
Kebangkitan yang hebat, Chuck!

1578
01:09:51,941 --> 01:09:54,537
<i>Kalau aku Mane, aku 'kan gemetar
di sepatu kudaku</i>

1579
01:09:54,562 --> 01:09:56,731
<i>karena Thorns
sedang mengincarnya.</i>

1580
01:09:56,864 --> 01:10:00,200
<i>♪ Tampaknya Si Poni
Menjadi Si Palsu... ♪</i>

1581
01:10:00,333 --> 01:10:01,779
Apa kita sepakat?

1582
01:10:03,705 --> 01:10:04,656
Bagus.

1583
01:10:04,681 --> 01:10:06,348
Pelatih Dennis,
bagaimana komentar Anda

1584
01:10:06,373 --> 01:10:08,176
soal kebangkitan tim
yang luar biasa ini?

1585
01:10:08,308 --> 01:10:09,510
Bagaimana rasanya, Dennis?

1586
01:10:09,644 --> 01:10:12,345
Rasanya seperti kemenangan!

1587
01:10:15,341 --> 01:10:21,361
<i>♪ Ini lebih dari sekadar
apa yang terlihat ♪</i>

1588
01:10:21,522 --> 01:10:23,024
Hore!

1589
01:10:23,157 --> 01:10:25,633
Tak tahu burung unta
bisa sekeren itu.

1590
01:10:25,658 --> 01:10:26,468
Kulihat kau, Olivia.

1591
01:10:26,493 --> 01:10:27,595
Kau tahu kata orang,

1592
01:10:27,729 --> 01:10:31,380
burung dengan bulu sejenis
terlihat keren bersama.

1593
01:10:32,107 --> 01:10:34,088
Archie sungguh memikat.

1594
01:10:34,862 --> 01:10:38,599
Ya, Kawan.
Aku terlihat dan bermain bagus.

1595
01:10:39,707 --> 01:10:43,720
Jika Modo lebih memikat lagi,
dia 'kan memakan dirinya sendiri.

1596
01:10:43,745 --> 01:10:45,580
Luar biasa. Suka sekali.

1597
01:10:45,713 --> 01:10:46,881
Uh...

1598
01:10:47,014 --> 01:10:48,983
Aku segera kembali.

1599
01:10:50,218 --> 01:10:51,986
Ada yang tahu Jett di mana?

1600
01:10:52,386 --> 01:10:53,496
Aku 'kan menjemputnya.

1601
01:10:53,521 --> 01:10:55,223
<i>Dari Vineland Thorns,</i>

1602
01:10:55,355 --> 01:10:57,825
<i>pemain bertahan, Jett Fillmore!</i>

1603
01:10:57,959 --> 01:10:59,794
Kujual tim ini.

1604
01:10:59,927 --> 01:11:03,731
Thorns yang baru pindah
ke Sunken City.

1605
01:11:03,865 --> 01:11:05,499
Maaf, apa?

1606
01:11:05,633 --> 01:11:06,768
Kau bercanda.

1607
01:11:06,901 --> 01:11:10,059
Aku tak pernah bercanda
soal uang, Sayang.

1608
01:11:10,084 --> 01:11:13,182
Kubawa Will ke tim ini
untuk menarik penonton,

1609
01:11:13,207 --> 01:11:16,202
tapi tak kusangka kalian
benar-benar menang.

1610
01:11:16,369 --> 01:11:18,154
Kujual selagi harganya
sedang bagus.

1611
01:11:18,179 --> 01:11:20,556
Apa yang 'kan terjadi
pada tim ini?

1612
01:11:20,581 --> 01:11:25,452
Oh, mereka semua diberhentikan.
Pembersihan total.

1613
01:11:25,741 --> 01:11:27,625
Dan soal kau...

1614
01:11:29,223 --> 01:11:35,395
Kupastikan pemilik baru tahu
soal kondisi fisikmu yang ringkih.

1615
01:11:35,748 --> 01:11:38,117
Dan tak mengejutkan,

1616
01:11:38,142 --> 01:11:40,543
mereka tak mau
membuang uang

1617
01:11:40,568 --> 01:11:43,704
untuk pemain tua yang payah

1618
01:11:43,838 --> 01:11:47,526
yang takkan pernah meraih trofi!

1619
01:11:47,551 --> 01:11:48,308
Oh.

1620
01:11:48,441 --> 01:11:52,847
Beritahu timmu untuk kemasi
loker usai kalian kalah.

1621
01:11:53,088 --> 01:11:57,059
Nikmati masa
pensiun dinimu, Jett.

1622
01:11:57,363 --> 01:12:00,100
Hei, semoga beruntung
malam ini.

1623
01:12:04,067 --> 01:12:06,169
Jett, Flo menjual Thorns?

1624
01:12:06,194 --> 01:12:07,804
Kau menguping
pembicaraanku?

1625
01:12:07,829 --> 01:12:09,180
- Kita harus beritahu tim.
- Tidak,

1626
01:12:09,205 --> 01:12:10,472
setelah pertandingan saja.

1627
01:12:10,497 --> 01:12:12,033
Jika sekarang,
mental mereka akan jatuh.

1628
01:12:12,058 --> 01:12:13,226
Ini berimbas pada kita semua.

1629
01:12:13,251 --> 01:12:15,812
Apa pun yang terjadi,
kita harus hadapi bersama.

1630
01:12:15,837 --> 01:12:18,447
Siapa kapten tim di sini?
Kau atau aku?

1631
01:12:18,472 --> 01:12:20,706
Jett.
Setelah pertandingan.

1632
01:12:24,219 --> 01:12:26,155
<i>Selamat datang di Cryosphere.</i>

1633
01:12:26,289 --> 01:12:28,758
<i>Malam ini,
Shivers menghadapi Thorns</i>

1634
01:12:28,783 --> 01:12:30,685
<i>di babak semifinal.</i>

1635
01:12:30,710 --> 01:12:33,286
<i>Pemenang melaju bangga
ke babak final</i>

1636
01:12:33,321 --> 01:12:36,933
<i>tuk berebut takhta juara
dan kejayaan abadi.</i>

1637
01:12:36,958 --> 01:12:40,382
<i>Pecundang? Terbuang ke
tong sampah sejarah.</i>

1638
01:12:40,407 --> 01:12:42,117
<i>Ini bukan sekadar laga.</i>

1639
01:12:42,142 --> 01:12:44,113
<i>Ini adalah penghakiman.</i>

1640
01:12:51,088 --> 01:12:53,943
Lenny,
kau ingin dijual?

1641
01:12:54,084 --> 01:12:55,515
Hei, hei, Jett, kau oke?

1642
01:12:55,540 --> 01:12:57,053
Fokuslah bertanding.

1643
01:12:57,078 --> 01:12:59,295
Jangan cemas.
Kita balas nanti.

1644
01:12:59,320 --> 01:13:00,423
<b><font color="#ffed2f">PUTARAN KE-2</font></b>

1645
01:13:00,480 --> 01:13:02,250
Olivia.

1646
01:13:03,056 --> 01:13:03,936
Satu operan lagi.

1647
01:13:03,961 --> 01:13:05,528
Lain kali jika ingin
menembak, jangan.

1648
01:13:06,521 --> 01:13:07,955
Maafkan aku, Jett.

1649
01:13:08,089 --> 01:13:10,191
<i>Babak pertama berakhir.</i>

1650
01:13:11,726 --> 01:13:12,727
Mungkin sebaiknya
beritahu mereka sekarang.

1651
01:13:12,771 --> 01:13:14,480
Setelah pertandingan.

1652
01:13:14,613 --> 01:13:15,487
<b><font color="#ffed2f">PUTARAN KE-4</font></b>

1653
01:13:23,197 --> 01:13:25,029
Jangan cederai
dirimu, Nenek.

1654
01:13:25,061 --> 01:13:27,041
Tangkap! Ya!

1655
01:13:28,672 --> 01:13:31,076
<i>Oh! Pukulan telak!</i>

1656
01:13:31,101 --> 01:13:33,101
<i>Harris lambat tuk bangkit.</i>

1657
01:13:33,431 --> 01:13:34,949
Gagal sudah trofi itu.

1658
01:13:35,248 --> 01:13:35,870
Terima kasih.

1659
01:13:35,902 --> 01:13:37,556
<i>Thorns tertinggal 15 angka</i>

1660
01:13:37,581 --> 01:13:38,413
<i>di akhir kuarter 4.</i>

1661
01:13:38,444 --> 01:13:41,495
<i>Kondisi memburuk tuk
harapan mereka di playoff.</i>

1662
01:13:42,173 --> 01:13:44,001
Apa yang terjadi di sana?

1663
01:13:44,026 --> 01:13:46,796
Jett, beritahu mereka.
Mereka berhak tahu.

1664
01:13:46,821 --> 01:13:48,044
Apa kukatakan tadi?

1665
01:13:48,069 --> 01:13:50,264
Flo menjual tim
ke Sunken City.

1666
01:13:50,303 --> 01:13:52,261
Tiada yang ikut pindah.

1667
01:13:52,286 --> 01:13:53,876
Apa dia boleh begitu? Apa itu legal?

1668
01:13:53,901 --> 01:13:55,678
Kita sedang hebat. Baru saja kompak.

1669
01:13:55,703 --> 01:13:57,505
- Dia menjual tim kita?
- Ada aturannya.

1670
01:13:57,530 --> 01:13:58,872
<i>Bisa jadi legenda, malah...</i>

1671
01:13:59,701 --> 01:14:05,304
<i>Pemain payah yang takkan
pernah raih trofi!</i>

1672
01:14:05,357 --> 01:14:07,571
Operkan bola padaku.

1673
01:14:07,596 --> 01:14:09,331
Aku tak mau kalah begini.

1674
01:14:09,356 --> 01:14:11,631
Maksudmu "kita"?

1675
01:14:11,656 --> 01:14:13,658
Aku tahu tatapan itu.

1676
01:14:17,858 --> 01:14:19,927
Apa yang kau lakukan?

1677
01:14:20,326 --> 01:14:22,104
<i>Skor masuk.
Thorns tertinggal 10.</i>

1678
01:14:22,129 --> 01:14:23,496
Ayolah.

1679
01:14:23,739 --> 01:14:26,008
Kita harus bertahan.

1680
01:14:26,033 --> 01:14:27,601
Seseorang kawal dia.

1681
01:14:28,736 --> 01:14:29,770
Ayo.

1682
01:14:31,105 --> 01:14:31,753
Oper!

1683
01:14:31,778 --> 01:14:33,950
<i>Pemandangan lama, Rusty.</i>

1684
01:14:33,975 --> 01:14:36,911
<i>Kini waktunya
aksi Jett Fillmore.</i>

1685
01:14:37,044 --> 01:14:39,443
<i>Jett menembak sambil lompat.
Thorns tertinggal 8.</i>

1686
01:14:41,983 --> 01:14:43,150
Awas!

1687
01:14:45,238 --> 01:14:47,073
<i>Selisih menipis jadi 5.</i>

1688
01:14:48,622 --> 01:14:50,191
<i>Beda 1 angka saja.</i>

1689
01:14:50,324 --> 01:14:51,392
Bola! Sekarang!

1690
01:14:51,525 --> 01:14:53,160
<i>Inilah penentu segalanya!</i>

1691
01:14:53,294 --> 01:14:54,962
- Archie!
- Berikan bolanya, Bocil.

1692
01:14:55,096 --> 01:14:56,297
Angkat aku!

1693
01:14:58,498 --> 01:15:00,901
<i>Will Harris tuk kemenangan!</i>

1694
01:15:04,782 --> 01:15:05,748
Ya!

1695
01:15:05,773 --> 01:15:08,642
<i>Thorns menang! Menang!</i>

1696
01:15:08,667 --> 01:15:10,869
<i>Mereka melaju ke final!</i>

1697
01:15:16,034 --> 01:15:18,803
Jadi sepertinya
kita melaju ke...

1698
01:15:19,973 --> 01:15:21,107
ke babak final.

1699
01:15:24,541 --> 01:15:27,711
Wah. Aku selesai.
Tim pun sudah dijual.

1700
01:15:27,736 --> 01:15:28,715
Ayo, anak-anak.

1701
01:15:28,740 --> 01:15:29,672
Aku tak mau lama-lama
di sini.

1702
01:15:29,697 --> 01:15:30,965
Modo juga.

1703
01:15:35,709 --> 01:15:37,978
Kau dulu pemain favoritku.

1704
01:15:38,692 --> 01:15:40,007
Sampai hari ini.

1705
01:15:41,288 --> 01:15:42,818
<i>Kejutan yang luar biasa.</i>

1706
01:15:42,952 --> 01:15:45,121
<i>Thorns meraih peluang juara,</i>

1707
01:15:45,146 --> 01:15:47,381
<i>tapi Vineland
kehilangan tim mereka.</i>

1708
01:15:47,516 --> 01:15:49,817
<i>Kuberitahu, Rusty, aku tak mau
jadi fan Thorns saat ini.</i>

1709
01:15:49,950 --> 01:15:51,419
<i>Pasti sangat berat.</i>

1710
01:15:52,783 --> 01:15:55,604
<i>♪ Ada kebebasan di dalam ♪</i>

1711
01:15:55,629 --> 01:15:57,873
<i>♪ Ada kebebasan di luar ♪</i>

1712
01:15:57,898 --> 01:16:01,168
<i>♪ Coba tampung luapan itu
di cangkir kertas ♪</i>

1713
01:16:04,374 --> 01:16:07,143
<i>♪ Pertempuran ada di depan ♪</i>

1714
01:16:07,208 --> 01:16:09,310
<i>♪ Banyak perang yang kalah ♪</i>

1715
01:16:09,403 --> 01:16:11,072
<i>♪ Tapi kau takkan lihat
ujung jalan ini ♪</i>

1716
01:16:11,205 --> 01:16:14,608
<i>♪ Selama kau berkelana
bersamaku ♪</i>

1717
01:16:15,181 --> 01:16:17,341
<i>♪ Hei kini, hei kini ♪</i>

1718
01:16:17,366 --> 01:16:20,285
<i>♪ Jangan bermimpi ini usai ♪</i>

1719
01:16:20,310 --> 01:16:23,156
<i>♪ Hei kini, hei kini ♪</i>

1720
01:16:23,181 --> 01:16:25,549
<i>♪ Saat dunia menghimpit ♪</i>

1721
01:16:26,020 --> 01:16:29,290
<i>♪ Mereka datang menghampiri ♪</i>

1722
01:16:29,315 --> 01:16:32,318
<i>♪ Tuk pisahkan kita ♪</i>

1723
01:16:32,561 --> 01:16:36,263
<i>♪ Kita tahu mereka takkan menang ♪</i>

1724
01:16:39,033 --> 01:16:41,769
<i>♪ Kuderek mobilku sekarang ♪</i>

1725
01:16:41,902 --> 01:16:43,904
<i>♪ Atapnya berlubang ♪</i>

1726
01:16:44,038 --> 01:16:46,107
<i>♪ Hartaku membuatku curiga ♪</i>

1727
01:16:46,240 --> 01:16:48,709
<i>♪ Tapi tiada bukti ♪</i>

1728
01:16:50,691 --> 01:16:52,825
<i>♪ Di koran hari ini ♪</i>

1729
01:16:53,478 --> 01:16:55,517
<i>♪ Kisah perang dan sampah ♪</i>

1730
01:16:55,649 --> 01:16:59,453
<i>♪ Tapi kau langsung membuka
halaman TV ♪</i>

1731
01:17:01,496 --> 01:17:03,599
<i>♪ Hei kini, hei kini ♪</i>

1732
01:17:03,624 --> 01:17:05,259
<i>♪ Jangan bermimpi ini usai ♪</i>

1733
01:17:06,692 --> 01:17:08,260
Ayo. cepat!

1734
01:17:09,529 --> 01:17:10,598
Aku dapat!

1735
01:17:12,591 --> 01:17:13,767
Si mungil bisa main.

1736
01:17:13,901 --> 01:17:17,004
Whew!
Ya!

1737
01:17:17,138 --> 01:17:18,672
Mustahil.
Tunggu, apa itu...

1738
01:17:18,806 --> 01:17:19,940
Hei, Will.

1739
01:17:21,080 --> 01:17:22,883
Kambing? Bola.

1740
01:17:24,478 --> 01:17:26,780
Yo, bukankah kau harus bersiap
menghadapi Magma?

1741
01:17:27,171 --> 01:17:28,840
Kau tak menonton laganya?

1742
01:17:28,865 --> 01:17:31,260
Kurasa Jett tak mau
main lagi dengan kita.

1743
01:17:31,285 --> 01:17:33,520
Kuberani taruhan dia mau.

1744
01:17:34,533 --> 01:17:37,019
Hei. Bisa kita bicara?

1745
01:17:37,279 --> 01:17:38,200
Aku sibuk.

1746
01:17:38,225 --> 01:17:39,572
-Tidak, dia tidak sibuk.
-Ayolah.

1747
01:17:39,597 --> 01:17:42,111
-Beri... Berikan bolanya.
-Tidak. Bolaku sekarang.

1748
01:17:44,146 --> 01:17:47,671
Aku datang tuk minta maaf.

1749
01:17:47,696 --> 01:17:50,097
Oke. Kau sudah melakukannya. Jadi...

1750
01:17:50,122 --> 01:17:53,058
Kumohon, dengarkan aku?

1751
01:17:57,646 --> 01:17:59,837
Aku ingin menang.

1752
01:18:00,657 --> 01:18:02,124
Aku ingin meraih trofi itu

1753
01:18:02,149 --> 01:18:06,020
dan merasakan menjadi
seorang pemain hebat.

1754
01:18:06,540 --> 01:18:10,144
Saat Flo bilang
aku sudah habis,

1755
01:18:10,169 --> 01:18:11,771
itu... itu...

1756
01:18:12,435 --> 01:18:14,264
itu merusak pikiranku.

1757
01:18:14,289 --> 01:18:16,640
Aku terus memikirkannya karena
jauh di lubuk hati,

1758
01:18:16,665 --> 01:18:18,645
jauh sekali,

1759
01:18:19,309 --> 01:18:21,277
aku takut dia benar.

1760
01:18:21,666 --> 01:18:23,187
Aku pun panik.

1761
01:18:23,871 --> 01:18:26,048
Aku jahat pada kalian semua.

1762
01:18:26,073 --> 01:18:29,643
- Dan aku...
- ...minta maaf.

1763
01:18:33,047 --> 01:18:34,815
Tahu tidak,
dulu kupikir

1764
01:18:34,949 --> 01:18:37,484
jika aku meraih trofi
pada akhirnya,

1765
01:18:37,509 --> 01:18:39,610
cara mendapatkannya
tak jadi soal.

1766
01:18:39,853 --> 01:18:41,388
Tapi jika kau renungkan,

1767
01:18:41,717 --> 01:18:43,852
hanya itulah
yang terpenting.

1768
01:18:45,356 --> 01:18:48,262
Itu permintaan maaf yang bagus.

1769
01:18:48,503 --> 01:18:53,008
Tapi kau masih berutang
trofi pada kedai itu.

1770
01:18:53,525 --> 01:18:55,931
Sulit tuk menang
tanpa tim.

1771
01:18:55,956 --> 01:18:57,858
Mungkin aku kenal mereka.

1772
01:18:59,614 --> 01:19:00,749
- Ayah.
- Ayah badut!

1773
01:19:00,774 --> 01:19:02,243
Oh, syukurlah.

1774
01:19:02,376 --> 01:19:03,645
Anak-anak ini gila.

1775
01:19:03,777 --> 01:19:06,708
Bawa aku pergi.
Cepat, nyalakan mobil!

1776
01:19:11,563 --> 01:19:12,606
Yo.

1777
01:19:15,221 --> 01:19:16,123
Apa kabar, Olivia?

1778
01:19:16,148 --> 01:19:18,400
Ayo. Kita punya
laga tuk dimenangkan.

1779
01:19:18,425 --> 01:19:19,626
Ya!

1780
01:19:32,337 --> 01:19:34,231
<b><font color="#ffed2f">LAGA AKHIR</font></b>

1781
01:19:40,420 --> 01:19:42,559
<i>Inilah isi sebuah mimpi, Rusty.</i>

1782
01:19:43,057 --> 01:19:45,026
<i>Tim menjadi juara.</i>

1783
01:19:45,051 --> 01:19:47,120
<i>Pemain menjadi legenda.</i>

1784
01:19:50,057 --> 01:19:51,925
<i>-♪ Ayo ♪
-♪ Ya ♪</i>

1785
01:19:52,059 --> 01:19:54,094
<i>♪ Beri bolanya
Beri bolanya, ya ♪</i>

1786
01:19:54,119 --> 01:19:55,621
<i>-♪ Ayo! ♪
-♪ Oh, aku akan... ♪</i>

1787
01:19:55,863 --> 01:19:58,468
-Ayo, Thorns!
-Hari terbaik dalam hidupku.

1788
01:19:58,493 --> 01:19:59,908
Aku mulai merasa
bersemangat.

1789
01:19:59,933 --> 01:20:03,212
Tak peduli! Aku siap menonton.
Membuatku haru, Nak!

1790
01:20:03,237 --> 01:20:05,214
Ayo, Will. Maju!

1791
01:20:05,239 --> 01:20:06,975
Ayo, Thorns! Ayo, Thorns!

1792
01:20:07,000 --> 01:20:08,235
<i>Malam ini, Jett dan Mane</i>

1793
01:20:08,275 --> 01:20:10,118
<i>akhirnya menjawab
pertanyaan,</i>

1794
01:20:10,143 --> 01:20:11,604
<i>siapa legenda sejati?</i>

1795
01:20:11,629 --> 01:20:15,030
- Hitung 3.
- Akar menghujam dalam!

1796
01:20:15,716 --> 01:20:18,517
<i>Mari kita mulai, Chuck.</i>

1797
01:20:19,626 --> 01:20:21,028
<i>Luar biasa!</i>

1798
01:20:21,053 --> 01:20:23,422
<i>Mane berebut bola
melampaui Lenny.</i>

1799
01:20:27,442 --> 01:20:28,742
<i>Mane mencetak poin pertama,</i>

1800
01:20:28,767 --> 01:20:31,282
<i>memberi peringatan keras
pada Thorns.</i>

1801
01:20:34,177 --> 01:20:37,046
Kau terlalu mungil.

1802
01:20:37,451 --> 01:20:40,922
Ayo, Will.
Tunjukkan siapa yang mungil.

1803
01:20:45,512 --> 01:20:47,013
Tatap aku.

1804
01:20:48,293 --> 01:20:50,143
<i>Jett memberi operan manis.</i>

1805
01:20:50,168 --> 01:20:51,169
<i>Thorns membalas.</i>

1806
01:20:51,194 --> 01:20:52,595
Ya!

1807
01:20:52,620 --> 01:20:54,488
<i>Saat kuarter 1
segera usai,</i>

1808
01:20:54,622 --> 01:20:56,629
<i>permainan masih sengit.</i>

1809
01:20:56,661 --> 01:20:59,569
Harusnya kita
melumat bodoh ini.

1810
01:20:59,594 --> 01:21:04,261
Habisi mereka jika perlu,
tapi pertahankan keunggulan.

1811
01:21:04,745 --> 01:21:06,251
<b><font color="#ffed2f">PUTARAN KE-2</font></b>

1812
01:21:07,039 --> 01:21:08,040
<i>Harris menyerang balik!</i>

1813
01:21:08,832 --> 01:21:09,986
Tidak hari ini!

1814
01:21:10,011 --> 01:21:11,980
-Will, awas!
-Huh?

1815
01:21:13,620 --> 01:21:15,421
<i>Ow! Benturan keras pada Jett.</i>

1816
01:21:15,548 --> 01:21:16,917
<i>Tiada pelanggaran.</i>

1817
01:21:18,559 --> 01:21:19,713
Apa?

1818
01:21:23,243 --> 01:21:24,679
Oh, Tidak.

1819
01:21:24,704 --> 01:21:26,515
<b><font color="#ffed2f">WAKTU ISTIRAHAT</font></b>

1820
01:21:27,988 --> 01:21:30,124
Cedera ini bisa
menghentikanmu selamanya.

1821
01:21:30,257 --> 01:21:32,359
Kaki ini 'kan lumpuh
jika kau paksakan.

1822
01:21:34,604 --> 01:21:36,286
Maafkan aku, kawan.

1823
01:21:36,311 --> 01:21:39,333
Jett. Aku tak bermaksud
membuatmu terluka.

1824
01:21:39,358 --> 01:21:41,771
Hei, hei.
Ini bukan salahmu.

1825
01:21:42,182 --> 01:21:45,053
Tapi sepertinya aku selesai.

1826
01:21:46,537 --> 01:21:47,517
Apa yang harus kita lakukan?

1827
01:21:47,542 --> 01:21:49,337
Kita tak bisa menang tanpa Jett.

1828
01:21:49,362 --> 01:21:52,346
Apa? Kita semua
memikirkan hal yang sama.

1829
01:21:56,795 --> 01:21:58,521
<b><font color="#ffed2f">BERMIMPILAH YANG BESAR</font></b>

1830
01:22:02,732 --> 01:22:07,862
Dengar, "akar menghujam dalam"
bukan sekadar sorakan.

1831
01:22:08,703 --> 01:22:12,274
Kalian tak tahu betapa berartinya
kalian bagi kota ini.

1832
01:22:12,407 --> 01:22:15,845
Ibu menyuruhku bermimpi tinggi.

1833
01:22:15,979 --> 01:22:17,413
Dan bagi Vineland,

1834
01:22:17,438 --> 01:22:21,518
tak ada mimpi yang lebih besar
dari membawa pulang trofi.

1835
01:22:21,653 --> 01:22:24,521
Mungkin ini laga terakhir
Vineland Thorns.

1836
01:22:24,546 --> 01:22:26,571
Dan kita takkan menyerah
begitu saja.

1837
01:22:26,596 --> 01:22:28,558
Ya, kalian dengar pemula.

1838
01:22:30,556 --> 01:22:32,535
Mari bermimpi besar.

1839
01:22:41,854 --> 01:22:43,389
Apa itu Jett?

1840
01:22:43,456 --> 01:22:45,458
-Apa dia baru saja--
-Ya, Jett!

1841
01:22:52,693 --> 01:22:55,910
Jett, Jett, Jett!

1842
01:22:56,043 --> 01:22:58,312
<i>Tepuk tangan meriah
yang layak</i>

1843
01:22:58,511 --> 01:23:01,080
<i>bagi legenda
Jett Fillmore.</i>

1844
01:23:05,358 --> 01:23:06,875
Selamat kembali, legenda.

1845
01:23:06,900 --> 01:23:09,970
Jett! Jett! Jett!

1846
01:23:10,503 --> 01:23:11,373
<b><font color="#ffed2f">PUTARAN KE-3</font></b>

1847
01:23:11,398 --> 01:23:12,265
Archie.

1848
01:23:14,162 --> 01:23:16,330
<i>Harris bermain beringas.</i>

1849
01:23:16,795 --> 01:23:18,664
<i>Skor Thorns kini imbang.</i>

1850
01:23:19,065 --> 01:23:21,441
-Olivia!
-Aku yang tangani.

1851
01:23:29,503 --> 01:23:30,651
Akulah burung itu.

1852
01:23:31,030 --> 01:23:32,867
Akulah burung itu.

1853
01:23:38,199 --> 01:23:39,902
Dia bisa terbang!

1854
01:23:39,954 --> 01:23:41,889
Aku bisa terbang!

1855
01:23:41,914 --> 01:23:44,239
Dia bisa terbang?

1856
01:23:45,292 --> 01:23:48,938
<i>Olivia Burke baru saja
permalukan Mane!</i>

1857
01:23:48,963 --> 01:23:50,899
Aku tak percaya ini!

1858
01:23:51,031 --> 01:23:52,700
Olivia!

1859
01:23:52,834 --> 01:23:54,802
-Benar sekali.
-Ayo, Livvy!

1860
01:23:54,936 --> 01:23:56,838
Ayo, Thorns! Kita bisa!

1861
01:23:57,246 --> 01:23:59,414
<i>Bola si mungil!
Burung unta terbang!</i>

1862
01:23:59,439 --> 01:24:01,699
<i>Inilah tim Thorns
yang kita nantikan!</i>

1863
01:24:01,808 --> 01:24:03,977
Lihat siapa yang
jadi pajangan sekarang.

1864
01:24:08,016 --> 01:24:09,684
Waktu habis, Magma.

1865
01:24:09,857 --> 01:24:12,827
Saran dariku?
Jauhi media sosial.

1866
01:24:13,146 --> 01:24:15,330
Kita harus membalikkan keadaan.

1867
01:24:15,355 --> 01:24:19,594
- Di mana para penggila Mane?
- Mane!

1868
01:24:19,727 --> 01:24:22,229
Sepertinya ada guncangan hebat.

1869
01:24:22,470 --> 01:24:24,807
<i>Dengar suara penonton itu.</i>

1870
01:24:24,832 --> 01:24:28,201
<i>-Mereka menggila.
-Oh, yeah!</i>

1871
01:24:28,475 --> 01:24:30,277
<i>Ayo!</i>

1872
01:24:31,685 --> 01:24:32,832
<b><font color="#ffed2f">PUTARAN KE-4</font></b>

1873
01:24:34,107 --> 01:24:37,244
-Archie terjebak. Tak ada jalan.
-Aku tahu rasanya, Rusty.

1874
01:24:38,210 --> 01:24:40,279
<i>Lenny melompat tinggi.</i>

1875
01:24:42,315 --> 01:24:44,551
Jett tak bisa menolongmu.

1876
01:24:47,975 --> 01:24:49,401
<i>Pelanggaran keras oleh Mane.</i>

1877
01:24:49,440 --> 01:24:50,976
-Apa?
-Harusnya itu pelanggaran!

1878
01:24:51,001 --> 01:24:53,335
Wasit dan si kuda
bekerja sama.

1879
01:24:53,360 --> 01:24:55,637
- Huu!
- Ayolah! Itu pelanggaran.

1880
01:24:57,700 --> 01:24:59,867
Serius? Begitu caramu
ingin menang?

1881
01:25:00,001 --> 01:25:02,263
Apa maumu, bocah mungil?

1882
01:25:02,288 --> 01:25:03,858
Hei, Mane!

1883
01:25:04,171 --> 01:25:06,373
Dia tidak mungil.

1884
01:25:06,507 --> 01:25:11,278
Dia ukuran sedang!

1885
01:25:11,411 --> 01:25:13,447
Hei, bubar!

1886
01:25:13,581 --> 01:25:15,415
Biar kuhajar dia!

1887
01:25:15,918 --> 01:25:17,125
Tenang!

1888
01:25:17,732 --> 01:25:19,020
Jangan sentuh

1889
01:25:19,152 --> 01:25:20,638
rekan setimku.

1890
01:25:20,663 --> 01:25:21,764
Hajar dia, Ayah!

1891
01:25:21,789 --> 01:25:23,457
Buat dia berdarah!

1892
01:25:23,591 --> 01:25:25,335
Itu tontonan yang buruk.

1893
01:25:25,360 --> 01:25:26,662
Bicara saja sendiri.

1894
01:25:26,701 --> 01:25:29,104
Pelanggaran berat.
Nomor 34, keluar.

1895
01:25:29,129 --> 01:25:31,613
Kau bercanda?
Mane yang memulai.

1896
01:25:31,638 --> 01:25:33,292
- Mana hukumannya?
- Menangislah.

1897
01:25:33,317 --> 01:25:35,969
<i>Aturan mewajibkan Thorns
punya 5 pemain</i>

1898
01:25:35,994 --> 01:25:37,829
<i>-atau mereka didiskualifikasi.
-Pukul aku lagi.</i>

1899
01:25:39,947 --> 01:25:41,236
Oke, oke.

1900
01:25:41,261 --> 01:25:43,263
Aku tak pernah main lagi
sejak dulu,

1901
01:25:43,309 --> 01:25:44,513
tapi kurasa aku bisa--

1902
01:25:50,798 --> 01:25:52,198
Mainkan aku, Pelatih.

1903
01:25:52,572 --> 01:25:55,276
Kita harus menang.

1904
01:25:57,759 --> 01:25:59,506
Jett, kau bahkan sulit jalan.

1905
01:25:59,531 --> 01:26:02,685
Kami tak bisa membiarkanmu.
Ini 'kan memperburuk keadaan.

1906
01:26:02,770 --> 01:26:04,074
Kau pikir mereka percaya?

1907
01:26:04,876 --> 01:26:06,710
Kira-kira begitu.

1908
01:26:06,735 --> 01:26:09,307
Hanya ada 3 detik
sebelum mereka sadar.

1909
01:26:09,332 --> 01:26:11,387
Tapi itu sudah cukup.
Kalian siap?

1910
01:26:11,412 --> 01:26:13,537
Aku sudah ingin memakai taktik ini,

1911
01:26:13,562 --> 01:26:16,027
tapi ada si keras kepala
yang terus menggangguku.

1912
01:26:16,052 --> 01:26:17,854
Taktik yang hebat.

1913
01:26:18,105 --> 01:26:20,073
Ya. Penantian ini sepadan.

1914
01:26:22,884 --> 01:26:24,620
Akar menghujam dalam!

1915
01:26:24,645 --> 01:26:26,651
<i>Thorns tertinggal 2 angka
dengan waktu 20 detik.</i>

1916
01:26:26,684 --> 01:26:30,165
<i>Jett pertaruhkan segalanya.
Sungguh pejuang sejati!</i>

1917
01:26:30,190 --> 01:26:31,810
Dengar. Kawal dia berdua.

1918
01:26:31,843 --> 01:26:33,536
Bertiga jika perlu.

1919
01:26:33,561 --> 01:26:35,971
Jangan lepaskan dia
dari pandangan.

1920
01:26:35,996 --> 01:26:38,716
<i>Jett sedang cedera.
Lapangan tidak stabil.</i>

1921
01:26:38,741 --> 01:26:41,010
<i>Masihkah ia jadi pilihan
tembakan terakhir?</i>

1922
01:26:41,041 --> 01:26:44,826
<i>Meski kiamat menghampiri
kita semua,</i>

1923
01:26:44,857 --> 01:26:47,835
<i>aku tetap memilih Fillmore!</i>

1924
01:27:04,125 --> 01:27:05,659
Ah!

1925
01:27:29,636 --> 01:27:30,806
Will!

1926
01:27:32,787 --> 01:27:34,622
Ayo. Lewati aku.

1927
01:27:34,756 --> 01:27:35,957
Aku tidak perlu melakukannya.

1928
01:28:09,866 --> 01:28:12,434
Sahabat kita baru saja meraih Claw.

1929
01:28:12,459 --> 01:28:15,495
- Itulah jagoanku!
- Peluk aku, Daryl.

1930
01:28:15,738 --> 01:28:18,107
<i>Untuk pertama kalinya
dalam 50 tahun,</i>

1931
01:28:18,132 --> 01:28:20,184
Vineland Thorns
menjadi juara!

1932
01:28:20,209 --> 01:28:22,323
Keajaiban bisa terjadi, Kawan.

1933
01:28:22,348 --> 01:28:26,448
Aku suka olahraga ini.
Dan aku sayang kau, Rusty.

1934
01:28:27,712 --> 01:28:30,948
Aku juga sayang kau, Chuckles.

1935
01:28:37,350 --> 01:28:39,591
Anak pintar, Will! Mwah!

1936
01:28:39,616 --> 01:28:40,449
Sayang!

1937
01:28:40,474 --> 01:28:43,710
Mari kita membuat
12 anak lagi.

1938
01:28:44,192 --> 01:28:45,208
Ha-ha!

1939
01:28:45,233 --> 01:28:49,438
10 tahun, 10 tim,
1 Claw, Sayang!

1940
01:28:49,831 --> 01:28:52,133
Kita adalah juara!

1941
01:28:52,266 --> 01:28:53,466
-Ayah!
-Ayah!

1942
01:28:53,594 --> 01:28:55,029
Ayah sangat keren.

1943
01:28:55,061 --> 01:28:58,665
Ayah memang keren, 'kan?
Ayah seperti...

1944
01:28:58,899 --> 01:29:01,335
Kami sayang Ayah. Mwah.

1945
01:29:01,360 --> 01:29:02,661
Ayah sayang kalian, Nak.

1946
01:29:04,296 --> 01:29:06,415
Hei, Mane. Laga yang bagus.

1947
01:29:06,440 --> 01:29:07,909
Biar kubantu bangun.

1948
01:29:09,258 --> 01:29:12,094
Hei, uh, rambutmu terbakar.

1949
01:29:12,119 --> 01:29:14,454
Apa?
Oh, jangan. Tidak.

1950
01:29:14,589 --> 01:29:16,413
Jangan rambutku!

1951
01:29:19,093 --> 01:29:20,728
- Will!
- Jett.

1952
01:29:21,096 --> 01:29:22,638
Kita juara, Sayang.

1953
01:29:22,663 --> 01:29:25,315
Oh, Jett! Kita berhasil!
Kita sungguh berhasil!

1954
01:29:25,340 --> 01:29:26,808
Bukan, kau yang berhasil.

1955
01:29:26,833 --> 01:29:28,567
Sepertinya Ibu benar.

1956
01:29:33,015 --> 01:29:34,757
-Jett, kau oke? Baik-baik saja?
-Aku oke.

1957
01:29:34,782 --> 01:29:36,451
Aku oke. Cuma tak bisa
rasakan kakiku...

1958
01:29:36,476 --> 01:29:38,982
...tapi aku juara, Sayang.

1959
01:29:39,875 --> 01:29:41,312
Tak pernah kusangka
hari ini tiba

1960
01:29:41,337 --> 01:29:43,331
saat Jett Fillmore oper bola.

1961
01:29:43,356 --> 01:29:44,496
Keamanan!

1962
01:29:44,669 --> 01:29:45,747
Tunggu dulu, Bodoh.

1963
01:29:45,772 --> 01:29:49,343
Waktunya bermain?
Haruskah kita hancurkan?

1964
01:29:49,772 --> 01:29:51,534
Hancurkan!

1965
01:29:51,559 --> 01:29:54,328
Kau tahu siapa aku?

1966
01:29:54,387 --> 01:29:55,705
Hei, kau benar soal Will.

1967
01:29:55,730 --> 01:29:57,599
Dia tambahan yang hebat
bagi tim.

1968
01:29:57,624 --> 01:29:59,460
Dah, Anak Babi.

1969
01:29:59,499 --> 01:30:05,006
Memperkenalkan
juara Roar,

1970
01:30:05,272 --> 01:30:09,951
Vineland Thorns!

1971
01:30:13,014 --> 01:30:16,050
Ya! Ayo, Vineland!
Maju terus!

1972
01:30:18,058 --> 01:30:19,641
Pasang tanduk, Semuanya.

1973
01:30:19,666 --> 01:30:21,188
Vineland!

1974
01:30:21,715 --> 01:30:24,017
Kurasa saatnya mereka
mendengar kabar dari...

1975
01:30:26,172 --> 01:30:27,907
sang legenda.

1976
01:30:28,369 --> 01:30:30,504
Will! Will! Will!

1977
01:30:32,106 --> 01:30:33,979
Si Kentang berhasil!

1978
01:30:38,082 --> 01:30:39,582
Aku... Aku...

1979
01:30:39,716 --> 01:30:41,217
Tak tahu harus bicara apa
saat ini.

1980
01:30:41,350 --> 01:30:43,619
- Ini gila.
- Kami sayang kau, Will!

1981
01:30:43,644 --> 01:30:45,680
Oh, wah, um...

1982
01:30:46,522 --> 01:30:48,624
Maksudku...

1983
01:30:49,095 --> 01:30:52,653
Aku menonton Jett main
saat masih kecil.

1984
01:30:53,333 --> 01:30:59,372
Lalu kubilang pada Ibuku,
"Aku 'kan jadi sepertinya."

1985
01:31:01,062 --> 01:31:02,781
Dan tahu apa yang gila?

1986
01:31:03,023 --> 01:31:05,775
Ibuku sungguh memercayainya.

1987
01:31:06,096 --> 01:31:09,512
Ibu selalu tahu hal-hal
semacam itu, 'kan?

1988
01:31:09,566 --> 01:31:15,276
Seperti ia selalu tahu bahwa
meski ia tak bisa di sini,

1989
01:31:15,518 --> 01:31:17,586
Vineland 'kan selalu ada.

1990
01:31:17,720 --> 01:31:19,722
Kalian mendukungku...

1991
01:31:19,747 --> 01:31:21,649
Will sudah merubah permainan.

1992
01:31:22,001 --> 01:31:24,361
Dan kalian selalu menjagaku.

1993
01:31:24,386 --> 01:31:26,075
Mbeeeek...

1994
01:31:26,465 --> 01:31:28,668
Kalian memberiku inspirasi.

1995
01:31:30,998 --> 01:31:34,468
Kita membawa pulang trofi Claw!

1996
01:31:40,194 --> 01:31:42,096
Dan meski Thorns

1997
01:31:42,162 --> 01:31:44,567
tak punya rumah lagi
di Vineland...

1998
01:31:48,434 --> 01:31:52,638
...tak ada yang bisa
merebut trofi ini dari kita!

1999
01:31:55,855 --> 01:31:59,125
Vineland 'kan jadi
juara selamanya!

2000
01:32:01,068 --> 01:32:03,437
Modo ingin bicara sesuatu!

2001
01:32:04,297 --> 01:32:08,868
Thorns tetap di Vineland!

2002
01:32:10,405 --> 01:32:13,342
Modo adalah pemilik tim.

2003
01:32:13,367 --> 01:32:14,711
Tunggu. Bagaimana bisa?

2004
01:32:19,857 --> 01:32:21,125
Pasang semua.

2005
01:32:21,150 --> 01:32:22,351
Pasang semua.

2006
01:32:22,376 --> 01:32:25,079
A-ha! Pembalasan telak!

2007
01:32:25,212 --> 01:32:26,847
Apa?
Biar kulihat itu.

2008
01:32:26,981 --> 01:32:29,683
Kau berikan tim ini pada
kadal aneh ini?

2009
01:32:29,925 --> 01:32:32,754
Wah! Ini benar-benar sah.

2010
01:32:32,779 --> 01:32:34,571
Modo bosku sekarang.

2011
01:32:34,596 --> 01:32:36,365
Itu tidak bagus.

2012
01:32:36,390 --> 01:32:37,892
Ya, Mama!

2013
01:32:39,294 --> 01:32:41,496
Modo.

2014
01:32:46,033 --> 01:32:48,537
- Nikahi aku, Modo!
- Jangan, nikahi aku!

2015
01:32:48,669 --> 01:32:50,471
Dengar itu, Vineland?

2016
01:32:50,725 --> 01:32:54,823
Sepertinya Thorns
tetap di sini!

2017
01:32:55,082 --> 01:32:58,111
Akar menghujam! Akar menghujam!

2018
01:32:58,218 --> 01:33:02,545
Akar menghujam! Akar menghujam!

2019
01:33:02,625 --> 01:33:03,925
Akar menghujam!

2020
01:33:04,051 --> 01:33:05,352
Akar menghujam dalam!

2021
01:33:05,486 --> 01:33:06,555
Akar menghujam dalam!

2022
01:33:06,687 --> 01:33:07,888
Akar menghujam dalam!

2023
